title: 074 - Back In Indy With A LOADED Folder Of Death
description: On today's show, the guys recap Pat's match against Adam Cole at NXT Takeover: XXX and how awesome it was to watch despite not getting the outcome we wanted, discuss how much air travel has changed since the beginning of Covid, taking dumps on airplanes, Zito not knowing if Chick-fil-A is chicken or burgers, the status of Calypso and Bonnie (it's not good), they bring in Billy Tubes for a CDL update and his new photoset featuring AJ Hawk, and much more in a loaded Pod FOD. Don't forget to subscribe to youtube.com/thepatmcafeeshow as we approach 1 million subscribers and our biggest giveaway ever, and send in your submissions to the Pod Fod @ThePodPMI on Twitter and Instagram. We appreciate you all, enjoy.
